## UI Components

- Choose proper ui components from `@/components/ui/`
- Do not use Card component unless I request it

## Icon

- Use `lucide-react` for icons

## Custom Components

- Always provide `className` prop and use `cn() from "@/lib/utils` utility to merge Tailwind classes

## Toast Notifications

- Use `import { toast } from 'sonner'` for all notifications
- Use semantic methods: `toast.success()`, `toast.error()`, `toast.info()`, `toast.warning()`

## Import Conventions

- Use `@/` prefix for internal imports

## Quality Standards

- Ensure `npm run lint` and `npm run build` passes before commits
- All in English
